title: Ep. #30 | TXT, WINNER, and SUPER JUNIOR
description:
Brian’s back with new jingles! This week, Eric reviews TXT’s “Runaway,” WINNER's “SOSO,” and Super Junior’s “SUPER Clap.”



This round of crazy ramblings includes the meaning behind Eric's fan club name, stories on feeling misunderstood in Korea, and reasons why the RAM in Eric's head is full #RELATABLE. Also, Brian and Eric open fan mail!



Make sure to subscribe to @daebakshow (IT’S FREE) and leave a comment, rating and/or review on Spotify, Apple Podcasts, Soundcloud, and YouTube.



Episodes are presented by @thedivestudios



Connect with us on all social media platforms @daebakshow and at http://www.divestudios.io/daebakshow !
